---



## Project structure

- `data/graduation_opportunities.csv`: input CSV sample
- `src/models.py`: Pydantic models
- `src/parser.py`: CSV parsing entry points
- `src/calendar_generator.py`: ICS generation entry points
- `src/cli.py`: Typer CLI
- `output/`: generated calendar files

## Setup with uv

Install dependencies:

```bash
uv sync
```

## Run the CLI

```bash
uv run opportunity-calendar generate
```

The default output file is `output/graduation.ics`.
